  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever you are in conversation, you can take a scroll, book or anything similar in hand and ask a creature one question. The creature must make a Wisdom saving throw vs your genjutsu save DC if it is unwilling to answer. If it fails or it decides to respond truthfully, the most accurate answer the creature could possibly give is immediately written in the book or scroll. Once you do this you can't do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
